<table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=10>
<tr><td bgcolor="#363636">
<a name="pestilence_scythe"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Pestilence Scythe</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">2H Slash</a><BR>
Damage per second - 6.88<BR>
Damage 16 - Delay 48<BR>
Weight: 9.9 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/necromancer/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">NEC</a>, <a href="/shadow_knight/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">SHD</a>, <a href="/warrior/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">WAR</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/vampiric_curse.shtml?spellID=667">Vampiric Curse</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
(Sv Poison +10) (Sv Disease +10) </font>
<BR>
Dropped in S. Karana by Lord Grimrot.<BR>

</td></tr>
